assessment_details.task_description:
Two to three questions will be provided in the week prior to the seminars on:

Earning quality and valuation;

Valuation topic presented by Professor Yohn;

Analyst research;

Valuation and income taxes; and

Corporate social responsibility and valuation.

Students will be required to submit a written answer to these questions at the end of each of the five relevant seminars. Each set of answers will be worth 2%.
